name: Corneo's Widowmaker (Overwatch) Embedding
description:
This is a textual inversion embedding for Widowmaker (Amélie Lacroix) from Overwatch.

Use corneo_widowmaker to activate. The eyes aren't that great with this embedding by itself (but it was a request so I want to release it anyway), so I recommend detailing the face a bit more in your prompt. Also as with most characters with different skin colors, the skin sometimes changes back to flesh color so it's a good idea to put blue_skin with some emphasis in your prompt.

Example images produced with OrangeCocoa available here https://civitai.com/models/4355/orangecocoa-5050-mix

Check out my other civitai models for more characters and sex positions! https://civitai.com/user/Master_Corneo

If you enjoy this embed, I genuinely love seeing your creations with it - you can attach them to a review if you're not aware (but not comments sadly)!
